{"tid":1595173,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］一向支持運動既外國記者Richard Scotford收到可靠情報","createTime":"2019-09-26T02:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T19:19:52.000Z","uid":261080,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fe6f232e80b99d120f9dfb3ef47cedc673525f7e","tid":1595173,"uid":261080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oVt84Pi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoVt84Pi.png&h=320ea7c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內文大意如下：<br />\n<br />\n警告：我收到非常可靠情報，9月27日至10月1日期間，香港將變成警政府狀態，警方將高度進擊任何形式、任何理由的市民集結活動。警方已獲授權，對一切看不過眼的人和事零容忍。<br />\n這種失智邏輯全為了利用恐懼阻止市民在十一國慶日上街集結。<br />\n在此呼籲示威者不要落單，務必團體行動，或策略性地以游擊戰方式進行活動，記得預早計畫撤退路線。"},{"pid":"329059749efef8eb545127affc38398ca86f1012","tid":1595173,"uid":258731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:19:50.000Z","msg":"［香港獨立！唯一辦法！］<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6MVGwi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6MVGwi.jpg&h=1ed93f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JWKL3KV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJWKL3KV.jpg&h=63206eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4dGKzOZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4dGKzOZ.jpg&h=bcba39e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqWCakp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqWCakp.jpg&h=6804524c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbFLjcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbFLjcd.jpg&h=70135473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【警世】不要再執迷於追求五大訴求<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1594691\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1594691</a>"},{"pid":"1e2dbac463843d2fc02649419daa12c9fefcf35f","tid":1595173,"uid":98842,"like":0,"